


Create a pod for a container:
===========================

apiVersion: v1
kind: Pod
metadata:
  name: sheel-pod
  labels:
    zone: prod
    version: v1
    name: sheel-pod
spec:
  containers:
  - name: sheel-ctr
    image: myimage:v0.5
    command: ["sh", "-c", "tail -f /dev/null"]
    ports:
    - containerPort: 5000
      name: http
      protocol: TCP 


Expose a pod:
=============
kubectl expose pod sheel-pod --type=NodePort --port=5000


